OL,3,CWater bills to rise further for
OL,4,Cmillions of households
OL,6,FMillions of households could see their
OL,7,Fwater bills rise further after the
OL,8,Fregulator Ofwat granted five water
OL,9,Fcompanies permission to increase their
OL,10,Fprices.
OL,12,FThe companies - Anglian, Northumbrian,
OL,13,FSouth East, Southern, and Wessex -
OL,14,Fwill provisionally be allowed to raise
OL,15,Ftheir bills by between 1% and 5% after
OL,16,Farguing the prices previously set by
OL,17,Fthe regulator were not sufficient to
OL,18,Fdeliver the investment needed for
OL,19,Finfrastructure.
