OL,3,CWater bills to rise further for
OL,4,Cmillions of households
OL,6,FAn independent group of experts
OL,7,Fappointed by the Competition and
OL,8,FMarkets Authority (CMA) said Anglian
OL,9,Fand Northumbrian should be allowed to
OL,10,Fincrease their bills by a further 1%,
OL,11,FSouthern by 3%, South East by 4% and
OL,12,FWessex by 5%.
OL,14,FThe five companies had requested to
OL,15,Fincrease bills to raise a total of
OL,16,F#2.7 billion in extra revenue, but the
OL,17,FCMA only allowed 21% of this figure,
OL,18,Fthe equivalent of an additional #556
OL,19,Fmillion.
