OL,3,CWater bills to rise further for
OL,4,Cmillions of households
OL,6,FKirstin Baker, who chaired the group
OL,7,Fof experts by the CMA, said: "We've
OL,8,Ffound that water companies' requests
OL,9,Ffor significant bill increases, on top
OL,10,Fof those allowed by Ofwat, are largely
OL,11,Funjustified," said Kirstin Baker, who
OL,12,Fchaired the group of experts by the
OL,13,FCMA.
OL,15,F"We understand the real pressure on
OL,16,Fhousehold budgets and have worked to
OL,17,Fkeep increases to a minimum, while
OL,18,Fstill ensuring there is funding to
OL,19,Fdeliver essential improvements at
OL,20,Freasonable cost."
