OL,3,CWater bills to rise further for
OL,4,Cmillions of households
OL,6,FThe extra money, which awaits approval
OL,7,Ffrom Ofwat, would be used to fund a
OL,8,Fmore resilient supply, reduce
OL,9,Fpollution, and reflect increased
OL,10,Ffinancing costs, the CMA said.
OL,12,FWater Minister Emma Hardy said: "I
OL,13,Funderstand the public's anger over
OL,14,Fbill rises ` that's why I expect every
OL,15,Fwater company to offer proper support
OL,16,Fto anyone struggling to pay.
