OL,3,CWater bills to rise further for
OL,4,Cmillions of households
OL,6,F"We've made sure that investment cash
OL,7,Fgoes into infrastructure upgrades, not
OL,8,Fbonuses, and we're creating a tough
OL,9,Fnew regulator to clean up our
OL,10,Fwaterways and restore trust in the
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,F"We are laser focused on helping ease
OL,14,Fthe cost of living pressure on
OL,15,Fhouseholds: we've frozen fuel duty,
OL,16,Fraised the minimum wage and pensions,
OL,17,Fand brought down mortgage rates `
OL,18,Fputting more money in people's
OL,19,Fpockets."
