OL,3,CWater bills to rise further for
OL,4,Cmillions of households
OL,6,F"CCW's own analysis suggests there was
OL,7,Fan opportunity to reduce these five
OL,8,Fcompanies' financing costs, cutting
OL,9,Fbills by around #41 a year, but
OL,10,Finstead the CMA has chosen to increase
OL,11,Ftheir rate of return," he added.
OL,13,F"There is a danger the customers of
OL,14,Fthese companies will end up paying
OL,15,Fmore, without seeing any additional
OL,16,Fimprovements in return.
